<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Per Christian Berg | Music | Christian Berg</title>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-primary">
    <div id="main" class="h-full mx-auto w-full lg:w-10/12 xl:w-8/12">
      {{> header }}
      <div class="relative">
        <img
          src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dvkodtgl9/image/upload/c_scale,q_auto:good,w_1440/v1629986340/perchristianberg.com/music/christian-berg"
          alt="Christian Berg hero image"
          class="h-screen sm:h-fixed object-cover w-full object-center"
          />
        <div class="absolute top-0 bottom-0 left-0 right-0 gradient"></div>

        <h1 id="header-title" class="w-8/12 left-2 title absolute -bottom-9 lg:-left-1.4 xl:text-title1 2xl:text-title2 sm:text-title2 text-screen text-white uppercase font-display">christian berg</h1>
      </div>
      <main class="my-24 flex justify-between flex-wrap lg:p-0 p-4">

        <section aria-label="Project and section headline" class="flex justify-between w-full flex-wrap">
          <div class="text-white font-body lg:w-3/5 w-full mb-16 lg:mb-0">
            Moving in the atmospheric landscapes from ambient to techno. Deeply inspired by nature and stillness.
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-display text-2xl uppercase text-opacity-50">discography</h3>
        </section>

        <!-- Album Skogsro -->
        <section aria-label="Album section skogsro" class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 my-16 lg:my-24 items-center gap-4 lg:p-0">
          <div>

            <h3 class="text-white font-display mb-8 text-2xl w-full lg:w-2/5">Skogsro</h3>
            <!-- <h3 class="mb-4 text-white font-display uppercase">Skogsro</h3> -->
            <img alt="Skogsro album cover"
                 src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dvkodtgl9/image/upload/c_scale,q_auto,w_1000/v1630335001/perchristianberg.com/albums/skogsro"
                 class="latest-release-img object-fit block mb-8 sm:hidden shadow-xl">
            <div class="text-white font-body w-full lg:w-4/5 mb-8">
              Cras auctor nunc ac dapibus volutpat. Pellentesque vitae commodo erat. Fusce
              sed augue ut massa laoreet dapibus. Nulla ac metus vitae massa tincidunt
              imperdiet. Donec volutpat iaculis diam, eu bibendum dui blandit et.
            </div>
            <a href="https://li.sten.to/skogsro" target="_blank" class="inline-block rounded font-display text-white ring-1 ring-white p-4 hover:bg-white hover:bg-opacity-10">
              Listen now
            </a>
          </div>
          <img alt="Skogsro album cover"
               src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dvkodtgl9/image/upload/c_scale,q_auto,w_1000/v1630335001/perchristianberg.com/albums/skogsro"
               class="latest-release-img object-fit hidden sm:block shadow-xl">
        </section>


        <!-- Album Ikigai -->
        <section aria-label="Album section Ikigai" class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 my-16 lg:my-24 items-center gap-4 lg:p-0">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-white font-display mb-8 text-2xl w-full lg:w-2/5">Ikigai</h3>
            <img alt="Ikigai album cover"
                 src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dvkodtgl9/image/upload/c_scale,q_auto,w_1000/v1630335001/perchristianberg.com/albums/ikigai"
                 class="latest-release-img object-fit block mb-8 sm:hidden shadow-xl">
            <div class="text-white font-body w-full lg:w-4/5 mb-8">
              Duis tincidunt erat non urna vulputate rhoncus. Curabitur et volutpat nibh. Nam
              at convallis lacus, non scelerisque purus. Integer et pharetra erat. Integer id
              metus metus.
            </div>
            <a href="#" target="_blank" class="inline-block rounded font-display text-white ring-1 ring-white p-4 hover:bg-white hover:bg-opacity-10">
              Listen now
            </a>
          </div>
          <img alt="Ikigai album cover"
               src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dvkodtgl9/image/upload/c_scale,q_auto,w_1000/v1630335001/perchristianberg.com/albums/ikigai"
               class="latest-release-img object-fit hidden sm:block shadow-xl">
        </section>
      </main>
      {{> footer }}
    </div>
    {{> menu }}
  </body>
</html>
